OL,3,CDo rising temperatures mean rising
OL,4,Cdeaths?
OL,6,FITV News Health and Science
OL,7,FCorrespondent Martin Stew explains
OL,8,Fthat while many enjoy the rare
OL,9,Fsunshine, soaring temperatures can be
OL,10,Fdangerous for the elderly and
OL,11,Fvulnerable.
OL,13,FIt's a familiar pattern.
OL,15,FThe sun comes out. The shirts come
OL,16,Foff. And the news alerts start rolling
OL,17,Fin.
