OL,3,CDo rising temperatures mean rising
OL,4,Cdeaths?
OL,6,FThe below graph from the UK Health
OL,7,FSecurity Agency charts 2022's summer
OL,8,Ftemperatures and excess mortality in
OL,9,Fthose aged 65 and over.
OL,11,FThe correlation is clear: excess
OL,12,Fdeaths rise in line with temperatures.
OL,14,FTo find out why heat can be dangerous,
OL,15,FI checked myself into the Altitude
OL,16,FCentre in London.
OL,18,FIt's where they train athletes to
OL,19,Fperform at high elevations and in warm
OL,20,Fclimates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
