OL,3,CDo rising temperatures mean rising
OL,4,Cdeaths?
OL,6,FIn the name of science, I agreed to a
OL,7,Fworkout in their heat chamber,
OL,8,Fessentially a treadmill in a sauna.
OL,10,FIt was an enlightening - and humbling
OL,11,F- experience.
OL,13,FAs they cranked up the temperatures,
OL,14,Fto a high of 39 degrees Celsius, even
OL,15,Fmaintaining a brisk walking pace
OL,16,Fbecame a challenge.
OL,18,FAnd by the end of it all, I'd lost
OL,19,F300ml in just 20 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
