OL,3,CDo rising temperatures mean rising
OL,4,Cdeaths?
OL,6,FEast London GP, Dr Farzana Hussain,
OL,7,Fsays that people who have long-terms
OL,8,Fconditions, those with heart or kidney
OL,9,Fproblems, people with diabetes, the
OL,10,Felderly and the very young are all at
OL,11,Frisk from high temperatures.
OL,13,F"As we're growing wiser with older
OL,14,Fage, our bodies are getting older so
OL,15,Fthe heart simply isn't as strong, the
OL,16,Fkidneys simply aren't as good, so it's
OL,17,Fjust about getting older and our
OL,18,Forgans having to work much harder in
OL,19,Fthe heat," Dr Farzana Hussain says.
